WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.290 --> 00:00:04.050
The Android ware platform
emphasizes depth and flexibility.

00:00:04.050 --> 00:00:08.580
Built on Android, it allows developers
to use familiar APIs to create useful,

00:00:08.580 --> 00:00:12.760
performance and imaginative apps
that run directly on the watch.

00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:15.970
In the spirit of Android, you have
the freedom to make substantial changes

00:00:15.970 --> 00:00:20.000
to the user experience, including
the creation of custom watch faces.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:23.250
There are three main categories
of experiences you can build.

00:00:23.250 --> 00:00:25.810
Notifications, watch faces and apps.

